0.3 - 29th Oct 2006
- Overhauled gkrellm_update_cpu (which was only reporting cumulative CPU time)
- Added GKRELLM_USE_MICROTIME constant to config
- Added format_bytes() to gkrellm_client
- Added get_interface_bandwidth_use() and get_disk_activity() to gkrellm_client
- Better error handling in the event of a terminated connection

0.2 - 15th Oct 2006
- gkrellm_update_sensors updates
- gkrellm_update_mail updates
- Added get_connection_changes to gkrellm_update_inet
- Added get_batteries/get_battery to gkrellm_update_battery
- Added get_total functions to gkrellm_update_cpu
- Bugfix in gkrellm_client::get_initial_update
- PHP Documentor comments

0.1 - 1st Oct 2006
- Initial release
